OL,3,CPolls close for the Gorton and Denton
OL,4,Cby-election
OL,6,FThe polls have closed in the Gorton
OL,7,Fand Denton by-election.
OL,9,FLabour won the Manchester seat in 2024
OL,10,Fwith more than half the vote but
OL,11,Fpolling suggests the party's candidate
OL,12,FAngeliki Stogia faces a tight three-
OL,13,Fway contest with Reform UK's Matt
OL,14,FGoodwin and the Greens' Hannah Spencer.
OL,16,FVotes are being counted in the Greater
OL,17,FManchester constituency, with the
OL,18,Fresult expected on Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
