OL,3,CPolls close for the Gorton and Denton
OL,4,Cby-election
OL,6,FThe outcome is likely to have
OL,7,Fimplications for May's local and
OL,8,Fdevolved elections and shape the
OL,9,Fpolitical landscape ahead of the next
OL,10,Fgeneral election.
OL,12,FThe by-election was triggered after
OL,13,Fprevious incumbent Andrew Gwynne
OL,14,Fannounced he was retiring on medical
OL,15,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
